FIG. 2 is a side elevational view of the utensil of FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 is a rear elevational view of the utensil of FIG. 1;


FIG. 4 is a bottom plan view of the utensil of FIG. 3;


FIG. 5 is an enlarged view in vertical section taken generally along the line 5--5 in FIG. 2;


FIG. 6 is an enlarged view in vertical section taken generally along the line 6--6 in FIG. 1;


FIG. 7 is a reduced side elevational view illustrating use of the utensil of the present invention as a bottle stopper;


